# Token Efficiency

- Keep responses brief unless the user asks for detail.
- Read only the files needed for the current task.
- Prefer focused single-file edits when practical.
- Avoid repeating summaries of unchanged work.
- Centralize homepage content in `lib/site-content.ts`.
- Preserve the static frontend-only architecture unless the user asks for backend work.
- Reuse existing section and UI components before creating new ones.
